<noinclude>
==Purpose==
If an image is available online, but cannot be uploaded to Wikipedia, it may be appropriate to use {{tl|externalimages}} to provide a direct link to the image and a (referenced) description of what the image depicts.

== Usage ==
<nowiki>
{{Externalimages
</nowiki>

|align=right/left

|width= number_of px  (standard 300)

<nowiki>
|image1=[http://www.xyz.jpg description_of_xyz] <ref> link_to_ page_where_xyz_is date_when_creating_this_link </ref>
</nowiki>

|image2= ...

}}




[[Category:Image insertion templates|{{PAGENAME}}]]
[[Category:External link templates|{{PAGENAME}}]]

[[ko:틀:외부 사진]]
</noinclude>

